title: Naruto Manga Volumes
description:
Naruto Volumes 1-42 (chapters 1-390)

Alright. this is my first torrent. I have seen other versions of this uploaded on here. The scantlations are from a variety of sources over the years.

Usually each volume is 8-10 chapters long. I figured that at 390 would be a good place to release it in volume form. Each volume is labeled at the beginning as to which chapters it contains (e.g 001-007Volume1 contains chapters one through seven)

I have removed a lot of the \&#039;bonus\&#039; materials that wasn\&#039;t included in the original volumes. Who wants 20 pages of naruto sauske slash in the middle of a volume? I have cleaned up alot of it, but if you run across any, please tell me which volume it is in so that I can fix it with the next release at volume 43.
